Currently, we add a patch while this patch is not fully tested. Please try tomorrow's build.

Also please assign enough permission to BIRT application. A simple way to do this is assigning AllPermission to BIRT. In tomcat, e.g, this can be done by adding following configuration into securiy policy file(conf/catalina.policy):

grant codeBase "file:${catalina.home}/webapps/%BIRT_APP%/WEB-INF/-" {
  permission java.security.AllPermission;
};

"BIRT_APP" represents the application folder of BIRT.
